            "q1": "How do control levels work?",
            "a1": "Control levels determine how persistent the app is with your reminders:\n\n‚Ä¢ Normal: A single notification.\n‚Ä¢ Strict: Notification + 2 reminders every 15 minutes.\n‚Ä¢ Critical: Notification + 5 reminders every 5 minutes with intense sound and vibration.",
